<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. A lien, a neute haw,
 A lungsietna ahin;
 Tuhin hung vek tau uo,
 Chieh mang kit ta lo di'n;
 * A vaigei tai hung kin mengun (2)
 Lungsietna kawt a hawn sung hin.

[V2]
 2. Isu hun sap lai hin,
 Paulap ding hawl loin;
 Mitduk gimtheite haw,
 Micheng cheng hung vek un;
 * Tuhin bang cheng hih zawh ei tai (2)
 Mun phapen le na chang thei ui.

[V3]
 3. Isu Kross thisan lul,
 A thawnin a va puoi;
 A thawkna cheng cheng chuh,
 Khat cha le a mang puoi;
 * A gam let nan thil lopipen (2)
 Hehpihna chun a bawlzo tai.

[V4]
 4. Micheng cheng hun khun hen,
 Belam No ma ahin;
 A min pak chiet u hen,
 A lopi bek ziek in;
 * Lei leh van mi kithuguol in (2)
 Kumsawt in chawian zel hitiu.</lyrics>
<title>TRUMPET</title>
<hymn_number>236</hymn_number>
</song>